headline: PandaDoc Takes Aim at Docusign with AI-Native MCP Release, Enterprise-Grade Trust, and Outcome-Based Pricing
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, September 16, 2025--PandaDoc, an easy-to-use document automation software provider for SMBs and mid-market teams, today expanded its AI infrastructure with a new server built on the Model Context Protocol (MCP). The release includes a robust compliance suite, deeper investments in integrated PandaDoc Notary, and the launch of new flexible and free plans that put decision making back in the hands of customers.
